1
00:00:04,500 --> 00:00:06,440
That untouchable woman.

2
00:00:06,470 --> 00:00:09,080
Spread her legs for me.
It was incredible.

3
00:00:10,010 --> 00:00:12,010
This feeling of conquest is amazing.

4
00:00:12,580 --> 00:00:13,980
Who are you talking about?

5
00:00:15,320 --> 00:00:17,080
I said you're all cute.

6
00:00:19,820 --> 00:00:21,350
No, I already...
I can't stop now.

7
00:00:23,360 --> 00:00:24,820
Until Reika gets this out of her system.

8
00:00:24,820 --> 00:00:26,260
I want to let her...
get all the revenge she wants.

9
00:00:26,790 --> 00:00:28,730
If this goes on,
word will really get back to my dad.

10
00:00:28,760 --> 00:00:29,330
It could happen.

11
00:00:29,660 --> 00:00:30,660
What am I going to do?

12
00:00:35,000 --> 00:00:37,900
Get up!
It might still be dangerous.

13
00:00:38,300 --> 00:00:41,670
Was this Reika's doing?
If so, then she's definitely...

14
00:00:46,250 --> 00:00:48,880
Her revenge...
has escalated, hasn't it?

15
00:00:49,250 --> 00:00:50,720
That woman...
she's gone too far.

16
00:00:51,250 --> 00:00:52,320
I'm reporting this to President Kurogane.

17
00:00:52,320 --> 00:00:54,820
Wait, we agreed...
to keep this quiet for two more weeks.

18
00:00:54,920 --> 00:00:56,460
Protecting your happiness...

19
00:00:56,460 --> 00:00:58,490
I told you...
is my duty.

20
00:00:58,530 --> 00:00:59,660
Several years ago.

21
00:00:59,690 --> 00:01:00,690
Stop.

22
00:01:01,260 --> 00:01:01,860
Please.

23
00:01:02,260 --> 00:01:03,500
If my dad comes here...

24
00:01:03,500 --> 00:01:04,500
...and does something to Reika,

25
00:01:04,500 --> 00:01:06,200
The reason I went as far as
to hurt Reika...

26
00:01:06,200 --> 00:01:07,930
...and break up with her...
will all be for nothing.

27
00:01:08,330 --> 00:01:09,900
Please don't tell my dad.

28
00:01:11,400 --> 00:01:12,400
I'm begging you.

29
00:01:14,270 --> 00:01:16,040
You're going to stop her from getting revenge,
right?

30
00:01:16,480 --> 00:01:17,480
Just a few more days.

31
00:01:18,210 --> 00:01:19,210
Give me a little more time.

32
00:01:20,050 --> 00:01:21,050
I'll...

33
00:01:22,050 --> 00:01:24,280
I swear I'll figure something out.

34
00:01:28,320 --> 00:01:29,320
Wait.
